fix: remove duplicate /api prefix, add session guards, cart refresh on order

- Remove /api/ prefix from all apiClient calls (client.ts baseURL already
  includes it) across admin, support, finance, inventory, staff, customers,
  products, reports, and auth modules
- Add useSession() + authenticated guards to all admin pages so API calls
  wait until the session is ready
- Clear cart (refreshCart) after successful order placement in checkout,
  PayPal return, so header badge resets to 0
- Clear guest_cart_id from localStorage in usePlaceOrder after order success
- Fix Toast provider: deduplicate "use client", use useRef for unique IDs,
  memoize useToast return value
- Refactor useCart to delegate to shared CartContext (single source of truth)
- Enhance CartContext mutateCart with revalidate option and fetchCart call
- Add session-token debug warning in apiClient request interceptor (dev only)
- Fix admin order detail: disable cancel button for terminal statuses,
  show better error messages from response data
- Fix admin product edit: section to div wrapper, localT typed as string
- Remove duplicate SELSA header from checkout auth page
